Sequence in which these scripts are to be called in the LitMod2D model directoty

1. make_mineral_wise_files.sh -- it will make a folder name Phase_diagrams in your model directory and will put all necessary files for visualization

2. python  phase_diagram_1D.py -- will plot depth distribution of wt%/vol%/moles at a distance point along the profile

3. python phase_diagram_2D.py -- will plot distribution of a selected property mineral wise along the profile
